ontend->currencyservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"RecommendationService\",\n      \"reason\": \"RecommendationService experienced a dramatic latency spike, exceeding 400x the normal average duration with context canceled errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Operation hipstershop.RecommendationService/ListRecommendations anomalies with normal_avg_duration = ~125ms and anomaly_avg_duration = ~56638ms. The error includes context canceled.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Experiencing increased latency during the issue window.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Increase in average response times for hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct, which escalated to ~14.5 seconds from ~10ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Latency spikes detected for cart operations, including GetCart and EmptyCart.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"hipstershop.CartService/GetCart operation latency increased from ~2.5ms to ~8.1ms; EmptyCart escalated from ~18ms to ~83ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Detected latency increases during supported currency conversions and retrieval.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"hipstershop.CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies latency grew from ~2.9ms to ~3.8ms.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据从UUID 10889e22-221相关的Metric数据分析，我们可以识别显著的异常指标和可能受影响的组件，从而更好地定位故障的根因。以下是此次分析的详细结果：\n\n### 检测到的异常指标\n- 包含变化率绝对值比较大的指标名称:\n  - `frontend rrt_max`\n  - `frontend rrt`\n  - `recommendationservice rrt`\n\n### 异常组件分析和原因推测\n通过异常指标的数据可以推测出几个重要现象：\n1. **Frontend 服务异常**\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 指标在故障期间激增，说明在这一时间段内部，前端请求处理延迟显著增加。\n   - **证据**: 正常中位值为 239,710, 故障中位值高达 60,001,805，变化率附近为 1.982。\n   \n2. **Recommendation Service 异常**\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 指标异常显著，响应时间剧升导致推荐服务性能出现大问题。\n   - **证据**: `rrt_max` 正常中位值为 10,763，故障中位值高达 732487046.56，变化率为1.9999。\n\n### JSON 格式输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"frontend rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend rrt\",\n    \"recommendationservice rrt\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in rrt_max and rrt during fault period causing service delays\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal median and fault median values for rrt_max were 239710 and 60001805 respectively\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Unusually high rrt_max indicating performance issues\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max value jumped from 10763 in normal operation to 732487046.56 during fault period\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此结果识别出异常指标，同时将重点放在服务性能异常上，而非node问题，因为没有直接指向node异常的指标出现。下一步建议针对相关服务进行详细诊断，比如查看具体服务日志、配置是否异常，或者监控环境参数是否发生变化。"}
